## SDD Workflow at a Glance

Phases: **W0 Bootstrap → W1 Change → W2 Review & Archive → W3 Steer**.

Phase | Commands
---|---
W0 Bootstrap | `/hx-constitution` `/hx-baseline`
W1 Change | `/hx-propose` `/hx-clarify` `/hx-design` `/hx-plan` `/hx-tasks` `/hx-analyze` `/hx-implement` `/hx-verify`
W2 Review & Archive | `/hx-review` `/hx-archive`
W3 Steer | `/hx-doctor`
Routing | `/hx-next` (suggests next command + flow)

Flow level controls ceremony: **`{{ flow }}` is this project's default**.
- `quick` — bugfix / small refactor: implement → verify → review → archive
- `standard` — normal feature (default): propose → plan → tasks → implement → verify → review → archive
- `full` — cross-cutting / API / security: + clarify + design + analyze + ADR
- `epic` — multi-capability: decompose, run children as full / standard

